\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 The morning sunlight streamed through the classroom windows, casting a warm glow over the rows of desks. Haruhi sat at her usual spot, her sketchbook open in front of her. Her pencil moved swiftly across the page, bringing to life a fantastical version of the classroom. Instead of her classmates, the desks were occupied by whimsical creatures\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 a fox with nine tails lounged in the corner, a dragon coiled around the teacher\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s podium, and a flock of tiny winged sprites flitted through the air. Haruhi\u8217\'92s lips curled into a small, smug smile as she added the finishing touches to a griffin perched on Aiko\u8217\'92s desk.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Aiko, sitting beside her, glanced over and raised an eyebrow. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You look unusually happy today,\u8221\'94 she said, her tone equal parts curious and suspicious. \u8220\'93Did something good happen?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruhi didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t look up, her pencil still moving across the page. \u8220\'93I submitted my Career Plan,\u8221\'94 she said, her voice light and sing-songy.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Aiko\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s eyes widened, and she leaned closer. \u8220\'93You did?!\u8221\'94 she exclaimed, her voice a little too loud. A few heads turned in their direction, but Aiko didn\u8217\'92t seem to notice. \u8220\'93What did you pick?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruhi finally looked up, her smug smile widening. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Tokyo University,\u8221\'94 she said, pausing for dramatic effect. \u8220\'93Fine Arts program.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Aiko stared at her, her mouth hanging open. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Seriously?!\u8221\'94 she said, her voice a mix of excitement and disbelief. \u8220\'93Did your parents approve of it?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruhi\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s smile didn\u8217\'92t waver. \u8220\'93No,\u8221\'94 she said simply, turning back to her sketchbook.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Aiko blinked, processing the information. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Wait,\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 what}{\f0\fs24\b0 ?\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 she said, her voice rising an octave. \u8220\'93You submitted it without telling them? are you crazy?!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruhi shrugged, her pencil still moving. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Maybe. But it\u8217\'92s my future, not theirs.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Aiko leaned back in her chair, running a hand through her hair. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Wow. I mean, I knew you were stubborn, but this is next level. What are you going to do when they find out?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruhi\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s smile faltered for a moment, but she quickly recovered. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ll deal with it when the time comes,\u8221\'94 she said, her tone casual. \u8220\'93For now, I\u8217\'92m just happy I finally made a decision.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Aiko shook her head, but a grin spread across her face. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re unbelievable, you know that? But hey, I\u8217\'92m proud of you. It takes guts to go after what you want.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruhi chuckled, her smug expression softening. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Thanks. That means a lot.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 The bell rang, signaling the start of class, and the room filled with the sound of shuffling papers and murmured conversations. Haruhi closed her sketchbook and tucked it into her bag, her mind already wandering to the future. For the first time in a long time, she felt like she was in control of her own destiny.}
